\ls2\ilvl0
\f1\fs26 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}When we receive salvation God gives us a gift of Eternal salvation \'96 both here and in the afterlife\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}But did you notice who the gift is being held by?\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}You and your salvation were put in the hands of God.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}You were never handed your salvation.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}You know why?  Because you can\'92t handle it!\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}And that is great news for everyone in the room right know who struggle with whether or not WE can lose it.\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls2\ilvl0
\f0\b \cf5 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}You see you can\'92t lose what you were never given!\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}You can\'92t let go of what you never were holding onto!\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}You can\'92t mess up what you were never managing!\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}You can\'92t mishandle what you were never handed!\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls2\ilvl0
\f1\b0 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}You can\'92t handle it\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf2 Let me ask you \'96 if you had $5 million for your kids future and retirement\'85and they were 6 would you let them have it all?  NO\'85you\'92d set up a fund and let someone else handle the money because even the best brightest smartest kid in the world\'85can\'92t handle that.  You\'92d end up with every lego set imaginable and no future.\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls3\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}And God is a good God and is not going to take the most important gift he can give you and allow you to mess it up!\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}You are God\'92s child and much like children who get inheritance\'85you get the gift and the benefit but it is not your responsibility to manage it\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}And as long as you think you have control of the situation, you will struggle with your eternal security!\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Because as we\'92ve said, you can\'92t handle your life!\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}You\'92re going to mess it up, you\'92re still going to make mistakes, you\'92re going to dumb bad things after you get saved!\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}But what Jesus is trying to reassure here in this passage is that when it comes to your salvation\'85you\'92re in the hands of God.  \
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}It\'92s not yours to mess up!\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
